name: Rebecca Galore
text: Pizza looked good but once I realized that ONE buffalo chicken slice was going to be $10+ I was not interested anymore.

name: Diogo Botelho
text: Pizza is very good. The service is terrible. They serve pizza and I waited 20 minutes! They are making more pizza instead of attending customers. Last time they didn't even give me a tray.

name: SirMikeProvolone
text: The food is mediocre while being pricy. It's not all that much better than Domino's, which is pretty sad

name: Isabel Clarke
text: Stood at the register for 10 minutes, while a gentleman stood with his back to me cooking, waiting to order. No one came so I left. It's a shame Pizza looked good.

name: Carl Beltran
text: This place  reminds me of Sbarro. Sometimes, one craves for simple food. Spaghetti with marinara sauce fits the bill
